These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
2 different pets are kept: ferret, fish
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: d&b, ambient
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, oliveros
House: gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. the cape-cod house is on the left or right of the oliveros-smoker##3
2. the owner of the fish is in an even position##4
3. the fan of ambient is the owner of the ferret##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the right of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Pet      | ferret  | fish   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient     | d&b   |
| Cigar         | oliveros | dannemann |
| House     | gothic-revival | cape-cod    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ebony, orange
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, dannemann
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: baseball, ice-hockey
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, soy-milk
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is in an odd position##4
2. the aristoff-smoker is the person drinking soy-milk##1
3. the person who likes orange is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Color          | ebony     | orange |
| Cigar   | dannemann | aristoff  |
| Sport           | ice-hockey         | baseball     |
| Beverage     | milk   | soy-milk    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, tulip
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, fishing
There 2 different types of food: carrot, artichoke
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: dubstep, folk
1. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
3. the person who growsdahlia is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| Flower    | tulip     | dahlia |
| Hobby         | fishing | traveling    |
| Food         | carrot         | artichoke        |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep         | folk    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-4::.
