The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, skydiving
2 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, gospel
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the fan of gospel is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Transport      | tram | bike       |
